================================================================================
                           组件层级结构
================================================================================

  UnifiedLayout (统一布局)
  |
  +-- Sidebar (侧边栏)
  |    +-- KnowledgeTree (知识库树)
  |    +-- DocumentMenuBar (文档菜单)
  |
  +-- Header (顶部导航)
  |    +-- DocumentOutline (文档大纲)
  |    +-- ShareDialog (分享对话框)
  |
  +-- Main Content Area
  |    +-- Dashboard (仪表盘)
  |    |    +-- DocumentList (文档列表)
  |    |
  |    +-- Editor (编辑器)
  |    |    +-- TextBlock (文本块)
  |    |    +-- HeadingBlock (标题块)
  |    |    +-- TodoBlock (待办块)
  |    |    +-- CalloutBlock (提示块)
  |    |    +-- CodeBlock (代码块)
  |    |    +-- ImageBlock (图片块)
  |    |    +-- TableBlock (表格块)
  |    |    +-- BubbleMenu (浮动菜单)
  |    |
  |    +-- ProjectView (项目视图)
  |    |    +-- KanbanBoard (看板)
  |    |    |    +-- TaskCard (任务卡片)
  |    |    +-- GanttChart (甘特图)
  |    |    +-- CalendarView (日历视图)
  |    |
  |    +-- KnowledgeBaseView (知识库视图)
  |
  +-- Side Panels (侧边面板)
  |    +-- ChatDrawer (聊天抽屉)
  |    +-- CommentPanel (评论面板)
  |    +-- VersionHistoryPanel (版本历史)
  |    +-- NotificationPanel (通知面板)
  |
  +-- VideoConference (视频会议)
       +-- MeetingControlBar (会议控制)
       +-- ParticipantPanel (参会者面板)
       +-- DeviceSelector (设备选择)

