================================================================================

                        +------------------+
                        |   Zustand Store  |
                        +--------+---------+
                                 |
     +-----------+-----------+----+----+-----------+-----------+
     |           |           |    |           |           |
     v           v           v    v           v           v
+--------+  +--------+  +--------+ +--------+ +--------+ +--------+
| Document|  |Comment |  |Project | |Meeting | |Knowledge| |  User  |
| Store   |  | Store  |  | Store  | | Store  | | Store  | | Store  |
+--------+  +--------+  +--------+ +--------+ +--------+ +--------+
     |           |           |         |           |           |
     +-----------+-----+------+----+-----+-----------+-----------+
                         |
                         v
              +--------------------+
              |   localStorage    |
              |   (状态持久化)     |
              +--------------------+

================================================================================
                           技术栈依赖
================================================================================

  框架层:
  +----------+    +----------+    +----------+
  | Next.js  |    |  React   |    |  TypeScript|
  |   16    |    |   19     |    |   5.x     |
  +----------+    +----------+    +----------+

  UI 层:
  +----------+    +----------+    +----------+
  | Ant      |    | Tailwind |    |  Lucide  |
  | Design 6 |    |  CSS v4  |    |  React   |
  +----------+    +----------+    +----------+

  状态层:
  +----------+    +----------+
  | Zustand  |    |  React   |
  |          |    | Context  |
  +----------+    +----------+

  通信层:
  +----------+    +----------+    +----------+
  | Socket.io|    | LiveKit |    |  Fetch   |
  |  Client  |    | Client  |    |  API     |
  +----------+    +----------+    +----------+

================================================================================
